text: Pierre Lequiller (2013) Pierre Lequiller (born December 4, 1949) is a member of the National Assembly of France. He represents the Yvelines department, and is a member of the Union for a Popular Movement. ==References== Category:1949 births Category:Living people Category:Union for a Popular Movement politicians Category:Deputies of the 12th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 14th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic
